resources.string:
To enable notifications, you must first access the SMS settings for your DID on the VoIP.ms portal. Enable the "SMS URL Callback" feature and enter the following URL into the neighbouring field:

http://voipmssms-kourlas.rhcloud.com/sms_callback?did={TO}

Note that the developer's server will store your DID to forward callbacks from VoIP.ms to your device. See Help for more details.
